All Classes and Interfaces

Classes
Class
Description
BranchingSearch
Contains an advanced algorithms for searching pentomino configurations on a grid.
BruteForceRandomSearch
Implements a brute-force random search algorithm to solve the Pentomino puzzle.
BruteForceSearch
Implements a brute-force search algorithm to solve the Pentomino puzzle.
PentominoBuilder
This class contains all the methods that you may need to start developing your project together with the representation of the pentomino's pieces
PentominoDatabase
This class takes care of reading all pentominoes and their permutations from a CSV Information abpout the structure of the CSV file (also included in pentomino.csv.README) Each line in the CSV file defines one permutation of a pentomino
Search
The Search class provides functionality to find solutions to fit a set of pentomino pieces within a specified grid using different algorithms.
SmallBranchingSearch
Implements a reduced branching search algorithm to solve the Pentomino puzzle.
UI
This class takes care of all the graphics to display a certain state.
